7822 - Motion Picture and Video Tape Distribution Summary > CRUNCHYROLL PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover computers and computer peripheral equipment and software. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. CRUNCHYROLL PTY LTD is headquartered in Melbourne, Victoria. It is headed by director Rahul Phaneendra Purini. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $30.83 million. Its net profit totalled $5.07 million. CRUNCHYROLL PTY LTD forms part of the wholesale trade industry sector.
